    "title": {
      "rendered": "6 Reasons Why People Do Not Give to Charity"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://funraise.org/techreport-past-reports\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22723\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Do-Not-Give-to-Charity-Twitter.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Do-Not-Give-to-Charity-Twitter.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Do-Not-Give-to-Charity-Twitter.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>7,106 people worldwide participated in the survey for the <a href=\"https://www.funraise.org/giving-report/past-reports\"><strong>2018 Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></a>. Of those, 1,049 responded that they had not given to charity within the last 12 months. Here are six reasons why:</p>\n<p><strong>1)</strong>\u00a043% responded that they do not give to charity because they do not have the financial resources.<br />\n<strong>2)</strong>\u00a020% volunteer in lieu of making donations.<br />\n<strong>3)</strong>\u00a017% donate goods and/or services in lieu of making a donation.<br />\n<strong>4)</strong>\u00a012% don\u2019t trust organizations to spend their money well.<br />\n<strong>5)</strong> 6% prefer to spend their money on their family and friends.<br />\n<strong>6)</strong>\u00a02% don\u2019t believe that organizations make a positive difference</p>\n<p>Furthermore, 52% of these non-donors said it was unlikely that they would donate to charity in the next 12 months. That said, those that do not give money to charity, do participate in civic life and are involved in charitable programs &#8211; just not as much as donors.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lifestyle Choices of Non-Donors Worldwide</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://funraise.org/techreport-past-reports\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22719\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Lifestyle-Choices-Non-donors.jpg?resize=600%2C305\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Lifestyle-Choices-Non-donors.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Lifestyle-Choices-Non-donors.jpg?resize=300%2C153&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lifestyle Choices of Donors Worldwide</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://funraise.org/techreport-past-reports\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22720\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Lifestyle-Choices-Donors.jpg?resize=600%2C334\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Lifestyle-Choices-Donors.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Lifestyle-Choices-Donors.jpg?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>For more insight in to global trends in giving, please download the <a href=\"https://www.funraise.org/giving-report/past-reports\"><strong>2018 Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.funraise.org/giving-report/past-reports\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-22613 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Report-Blue-English-Twitter-600.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Report-Blue-English-Twitter-600.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Report-Blue-English-Twitter-600.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
